<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="genitive">whose</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 continued support for pagan deities and the fact that 
<REF ID="1481.9" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np-subj">
